<p style="white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, 黑体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 32px; font-size: 15px;">曾为不善言谈而失去一份好机会？</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, 黑体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 32px; font-size: 15px;">曾为不善交流而错失一位好伴侣？</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px;">杰明.富兰克林说：“<strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">成功的第一要素是懂得如何搞好人际关系</span></strong>”。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px;">一个人在社会上行走，要想达到无往不胜，首先得懂得处理好人际关系。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, 黑体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 32px; font-size: 15px;">我们经常会听到这样的叮嘱，<strong>做事先做人。</strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, 黑体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 32px; font-size: 15px;">不会做人的人，要想做成一件大事，是难上加难。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, 黑体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 32px; font-size: 15px;">人脉越宽，路子越宽，事情就越好办，几千年来，这已经被无数的实践所验证。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, 黑体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 32px; font-size: 15px;">当良好的人际关系成为个人无形资产的时候，成功的康庄大道已经打开。</span></strong></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">纵观社会现象，为什么有些学历、能力都不差的人，却会在人生发展道路上落后？</span></p><p style="margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">正是因为他们忽略了最重要的一种能力——</span></p><p style="margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑;">人际关系管理的能力！</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">而在斯坦福大学的调查中也显示：<strong>一个人赚的钱，12.5%来自于知识，87.5%来自于人脉！</strong></span></p><p style="margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">而人脉的维护不是靠心机，靠的是人际关系管理的能力！</span></p><p style="margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appEOYSm4kc8307/image/ueditor/86666300_1543994647.jpg"/></span></p><p style="margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">在职场中我们知道，建立良好的人际关系对事业的发展非常重要。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><strong><span style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">当拥有良好的人际关系处理能力时——</span></strong></p><p><section style="white-space: normal; border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 647px;"><section style="background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); box-shadow: rgb(136, 136, 136) 0px 0px 10px 0px; background-image: url('http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appEOYSm4kc8307/image/ueditor/80246900_1543994647.com/mmbiz_png/un1liav7oj8exicj4qmxvby1zaqgxgqic9l7dxoxiiaz1ico5icmpd4gscq3vh8iibia5plymk64j1l6k01qpe8k4db4w/0?wx_fmt=png'); padding: 15px 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; line-height: 20px; padding-right: 30px; background-image: url('http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appEOYSm4kc8307/image/ueditor/95811700_1543994647.com/mmbiz_png/fgnkxfgnnksxszkhgupudugwx2fi94lkja3mwpf67xgctykokukqihl68806xslfqt8jsz3uu74hnxiclooyiayq/0?wx_fmt=png'); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: 20px 20px; background-position: right top; letter-spacing: 1.5px;">1.我们呈报的提议更容易得到上司的重视与采纳；</p><p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; line-height: 20px; padding-right: 30px; background-image: url('http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appEOYSm4kc8307/image/ueditor/95811700_1543994647.com/mmbiz_png/fgnkxfgnnksxszkhgupudugwx2fi94lkja3mwpf67xgctykokukqihl68806xslfqt8jsz3uu74hnxiclooyiayq/0?wx_fmt=png'); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: 20px 20px; background-position: right top; letter-spacing: 1.5px;">2.跨部门的同事更乐意配合我们正在推进的工作；</p><p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; line-height: 20px; padding-right: 30px; background-image: url('http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appEOYSm4kc8307/image/ueditor/95811700_1543994647.com/mmbiz_png/fgnkxfgnnksxszkhgupudugwx2fi94lkja3mwpf67xgctykokukqihl68806xslfqt8jsz3uu74hnxiclooyiayq/0?wx_fmt=png'); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: 20px 20px; background-position: right top; letter-spacing: 1.5px;">3.在面对部属时我们会更具影响力；</p><p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; line-height: 20px; padding-right: 30px; background-image: url('http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appEOYSm4kc8307/image/ueditor/95811700_1543994647.com/mmbiz_png/fgnkxfgnnksxszkhgupudugwx2fi94lkja3mwpf67xgctykokukqihl68806xslfqt8jsz3uu74hnxiclooyiayq/0?wx_fmt=png'); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: 20px 20px; background-position: right top; letter-spacing: 1.5px;">4.与同事相处的关系更加融洽</p><p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; line-height: 20px; padding-right: 30px; background-image: url('http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appEOYSm4kc8307/image/ueditor/95811700_1543994647.com/mmbiz_png/fgnkxfgnnksxszkhgupudugwx2fi94lkja3mwpf67xgctykokukqihl68806xslfqt8jsz3uu74hnxiclooyiayq/0?wx_fmt=png'); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: 20px 20px; background-position: right top; letter-spacing: 1.5px;">·······<br/></p></section></section></section></section></section></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="text-indent: 28px; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">其实，几乎所有的人都知道处理好人际关系的重要性，但尽管如此，大多数都不知道怎样才能处理好人际关系，甚至许多人会错误的认为拍马屁、讲奉承话、请客送礼，才是处理好人际关系最好的手段。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">那到底该如何处理好人际关系呢？</span></p><p style="margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">你会不时的给关系“排毒”吗？</span></p><p style="margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">造成人际关系恶化的关键原因是什么？<br/></span></p><p style="margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">在人际交往中要中规中矩吗？</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">知名人力资源管理“实战派”专家<strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">张艳桦</span></strong>老师为大家带来<span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>《人人都应懂得的18堂关系处理课》</strong></span><strong>，</strong>解决人际关系的一切问题！</span></p><p style="margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑;">为你揭示人际交往中的那些微妙之处，让你在处理复杂人际关系时游刃有余。</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">做好关系管理，助力人生腾飞！</span></strong></p><p style="margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appEOYSm4kc8307/image/ueditor/17632700_1543994648.png" alt="张艳桦-封面.pn